sentences: Thomas L. Riis or Thomas Laurence Riis (born October 6, 1950) is an American musicologist and professor.
He has been on the faculty of the University of Colorado Boulder since 1992.
His book Just Before Jazz, devoted to African-American Broadway shows, received an ASCAP-Deems Taylor Award in 1995.
